            </div>
            <div class="entry-problem"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;">(마)에서 알 수 있는 용이의 심정으로 적절하지 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">않은</span> 것은?</p><div class="level4"><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">① </span>냉담함</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">② </span>비참함</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">③ </span>열등감</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">④ </span>절망감</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">⑤ </span>부끄러움</p></div></div></div>
